race.comment: LIVALITTLE (3) has been racing well without winning this preparation placing at his past three outings. Gets some weight relief with the 2kg claim and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. WHISKY TRAIN (7) has won over this distance range, gets some weight off and draws the inside marble. Ticks a few boxes. The well-related INSAIN JEWEL (12) (half to G2 winners Ninth Legion and Tsaritsa) best of the rest. Ran a good race at Scone two back. WILL IT SNOW (11) shed his maiden on resuming at this course. Got a long way back last start at this course over 1300m. Up sharply in trip on that outing and holds appeal.
